Modification relative to upstream Harbor v0.6.5:

  In src/harbor/agents/installed/codex.py, the function
  _build_register_skills_command() now copies registered skills into
  $CODEX_HOME/skills/ rather than $HOME/.agents/skills/. The previous path
  fell outside the writable area of Codex's default sandbox profile, so
  registered skills were not visible to the agent at runtime; $CODEX_HOME
  is the canonical Codex state directory and is sandbox-writable.

  Diff: 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-).
  Of those, 5 lines are an in-file modification notice (Apache-2.0 section 4(b))
  immediately above the modified function; the remaining 2-line change is the
  literal path replacement.

